Feel free to share, just make sure you tag us please!

node.text:
The United States Marine Corps operate two STOVL (Short Take Off Vertical Landing) aircraft. The McDonnell Douglas (now Boeing) AV-8B Harrier II and the new Lockheed Martin F-35B Lightning II. Both are extremely capable aircraft which is your favorite?! Presented in conjunction with This is Flight! 
#thisisflight #AirshowStuff #av8b #f35 #f35b #stovl #harrier #usmc #lightningii #mcasyuma

node.text:
While big airshows are great we really love small field fly-ins. Today we were at the Poplar Grove Fly In and Car Show. Attendance was huge and the weather was great. All sorts of flying going on at this great little local airport. If you ever have a chance check out Poplar Grove Airport, do it. 

#poplargroveairport #flyin #poplargrove #airshowstuff

node.text:
Little more Chicago Air and Water Show love. This time @pja.photo and @joeyhamerstudio joined forces for an awesome 106 shot GIF of the @navyblueangelsolos sneak pass from Friday. 😍😍

#repost 
My man @joeyhamerstudio put together this INSANE video made up of all the stills from my 106 shot burst of yesterday’s high speed pass. What do you all think?? Did he absolutely kill it or what??
@usnavyblueangels @navyblueangelsolos @navyblueangel8 @chewy1105 
.
#usnavy #usnavyblueangels #blueangels #blueangelsairshow #avgeek #avgeeks #avgeekoftheweek #militaryplanes #highspeedpass #sneakpass #chicagoairandwatershow #chicagoairshow #chicagoairandwatershow2021 #turnandburn #transonic #shockwave #aviationdaily #aviationlovers #avgeekphoto #airshow #airshows #f18superhornet #instaaviation #instaaviationphotography 
Special thanks again to @axisapartments for having us up to shoot the angels!! What a view!

node.text:
"Beale Air Force Base Open House October 31, 1981.
Lockheed SR-71A 61-7974 departed the airshow early in order to appear at two other airshows that day"

How cool is this?! SR-71 makes a few passes at home then heads off to fly over a few other shows. Nothing like the burners on the Blackbird! 🔥🔥😍

📷 - Richard Lockett of air-and-space.com
Go check it out! 

#sr71blackbird #sr71 #blackbird
#skunkworks #bealeafb #bealeairforcebase #afterburner #airshowstuff #TBT
